{"tid":1189350,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"假如你聽到家人講呢番話你會點？","createTime":"2019-06-06T18:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T08:50:22.000Z","uid":206511,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7fefa03961a06770db91fce0c2207825db33c6d6","tid":1189350,"uid":206511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:00:11.000Z","msg":"第一次開post 頂唔順了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本來我就可以唔洗存在係呢個世界<br />\n佢地因為發現得我遲先冇得落左我（開門見山同我講）<br />\n<br />\n假如你聽到屋企人講呢句<br />\n「我真係好撚後悔生撚左你呢個閪人出黎」<br />\n「我好撚憎你」/「你越黎越討我厭」<br />\n「我究竟前世欠你幾撚多野，呢世幾時還完就唔洗再見到你」<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n「廢柴 寄生蟲 垃圾 仆街仔唔死都冇用」之類聽慣曬<br />\n就算呢幾句都覺得難聽<br />\n但顯然已經唔係同一層次了<br />\n有冇啲人聽到會覺得無乜事<br />\n可唔可以教我點解心臟可以咁強大<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d460cff28ae32c689676bafff294f7771b9070d7","tid":1189350,"uid":15835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:01:07.000Z","msg":"你幾多歲 ?"},{"pid":"5ad8f13edf4f6e393c184a0c54a8b1777b57a28e","tid":1189350,"uid":206511,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"d460cff28ae32c689676bafff294f7771b9070d7","tid":1189350,"uid":15835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:01:07.000Z","msg":"你幾多歲 ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:02:22.000Z","msg":"19歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經由細聽到大 但今日真係突然好頂唔順"},{"pid":"507c904d5d81f041bc875a6957dec1321c770a6b","tid":1189350,"uid":7615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7cd7844707ce896258201b05e514b73af0fe65a","tid":1189350,"uid":254886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:04:27.000Z","msg":"因咩事會咁話你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787b99dfef01327d3e5f9ed8404a78e9953b